BBC.Glastonbury.2013.06.29.1080i.HDTV.h264-NX

Saturday 29th June 2013

Part 1: 16:00-18:00 (2 hours)
Coverage of the second day of the festival continues live from the heart of the Somerset countryside with hosts Mark Radcliffe, Lauren Laverne and Jo Whiley bringing you highlights from the myriad of stages from the festival together with some bespoke acoustic moments and a peek at what's going on around and about the massive Glastonbury site.

Part 2: 22:30-02:00 (3.5 hours)
Live coverage from the festival continues with Jo Whiley, Mark Radcliffe and Lauren Laverne at their home in the Park area with performances from the likes of The Rolling Stones, Elvis Costello, Primal Scream, Savages and Haim. Plus acoustic performances and a voyage into the weird and wonderful late night world of Glastonbury.
